						<summary>

						<p>Right pillar (top) in the Vishṇumaṇḍapa, Fort at Gandhakam.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1109. <hi rend="italic">(Navati-rudra).</hi></hi></p>						

						<p>Records the gift of land for the maintenance of a lamp for auxiliary deities like Vināyaka in the temple (not stated) by Mulukaṭi Pōtama-seṭṭi of <hi rend="italic">Dhanēśa-vaṁśa.</hi></p>						

